main event: Observers watched a star-like object travel across the sky and disappear in the SE.
interesting points: The object seemed to move faster than a commercial aircraft.,No unusual characteristics were noted.,The observers did not believe the object to be unidentified.,The sighting lasted for about 10 minutes.,The object disappeared to the southwest after being observed.
witness description: The witness had not seen a similar object before and was outside at the time of the sighting.
